    "description": "Inspired by the fascinating story of life on Earth, Creaturing - Sea Wonders allows you to create, control, test and share physic-based sea creatures and discover evolution through surprising challenges!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > CREATE</h2> <br>Use the flexible creature building system to create awesome physics based sea creatures of all shapes and sizes with all sorts of abilities! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878260/extras/2beb51741950e4d97376572b13d439d6.poster.avif?t=1726759626\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878260/extras/2beb51741950e4d97376572b13d439d6.webm?t=1726759626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878260/extras/2beb51741950e4d97376572b13d439d6.mp4?t=1726759626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DISCOVER EVOLUTION THROUGH SURPRISING CHALLENGES</h2> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> To survive as a crab, eat your own babies!<br></li><li> As a lobster, fight for a place to lay your eggs!<br> </li><li> As a pufferfish, create art to attract a mate! <br></li><li> And much more! </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878260/extras/01a25c698531e59183d4d59c9fca776f.poster.avif?t=1726759626\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878260/extras/01a25c698531e59183d4d59c9fca776f.webm?t=1726759626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878260/extras/01a25c698531e59183d4d59c9fca776f.mp4?t=1726759626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > CONTROL</h2> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> Move your creatures with the help of mechanical parts like joints and thrusters! <br></li><li> Control your creatures' behavior using sensors and neural circuits inspired by electronics!<br> </li><li> Test the capacities of your creatures in lush and beautiful underwater environments!  </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878260/extras/0cda93652aacc7be31536aa1b33950fa.poster.avif?t=1726759626\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878260/extras/0cda93652aacc7be31536aa1b33950fa.webm?t=1726759626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878260/extras/0cda93652aacc7be31536aa1b33950fa.mp4?t=1726759626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > SHARE</h2> <br>Share your realistic or whimsical creatures on the Steam Workshop!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878260/extras/3634bfbfc6fd106db6ac90afb83933d9.poster.avif?t=1726759626\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878260/extras/3634bfbfc6fd106db6ac90afb83933d9.webm?t=1726759626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878260/extras/3634bfbfc6fd106db6ac90afb83933d9.mp4?t=1726759626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
